datasets.name: dataset_4
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) AS `Daily Event Date`, MEASURE(`Total Clicks`) AS `Total Clicks`, `Control` FROM workspace.default.mv_hpx_events_model WHERE `Control` IN ('controlyourpc section viewallcontrols link', 'pcdevice core navigationviewitem id', 'pcdevicepage featurecard support core', 'pchardware core navigationviewitem id', 'profile avatar', 'settings core navigationviewitem id', 'strictlynecessarynotice snnview continuebtn', 'support core navigationviewitem id', 'navigator togglepanebutton', 'welcome core navigationviewitem id') AND `Event Date Time` >= '2023-05-01' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`), `Control` ORDER BY `Daily Event Date`

frame.title: Top On Press Events by Control
